  description: "\\large{A knife flashes in the darkness. You never see the face of your\n                    attacker. The adventure begins.}\n                    \\emph{Their spirits trapped by a cursed magical weapon, the heroes find\n                    themselves imprisoned in the surreal domain of \\Place{Aggarath}. Here, they\n                    must explore the mind of \\NPC{Chardath Spulzeer}, the insane lord of the\n                    realm. Somewhere in his shattered dreams and tormented memories lie secrets\n                    that may enable the adventurers to escape.}\n                    \\Product{The Forgotten Terror} is a new adventure for the \\Product{Ravenloft}\n                    campaign setting. It can be played as a stand-alone scenario or as a sequel\n                    to the events depicted in the \\Product{Forgotten Realms} adventure\n                    \\Product{Castle Spulzeer}. The unique nature of this domain and scenario\n                    makes \\Product{The Forgotten Terror} easy for the Dungeon Master to run\n                    without forcing players through a linear plot. Alternate endings allow the DM\n                    to link this adventure to \\Place{Ravenloft}, the \\Place{Realms}, or any other\n                    campaign world."
